originalText.text:
This review is long over due. I have used acupuncture and Chinese medicine for over two decades of my life and have seen many many practitioners. Qi Hui has been part of my maintenance regimen to keep my mental health and reproductive health balanced and calm.

He is one of the most patient and gentle practitioners I’ve been to. He has taught he so much about seasonal living, explains his process, and is happy to answer all of my questions.

Happy to recommend!

originalText.text: Qihui is the best!!! I’m so glad I found him here in NYC. I am a dancer so I’m very hard on my body. He has helped me through a bad ankle sprain and maintenance on a small meniscus tear. He even helped my digestion after the holidays. He is very knowledgeable and has a nice calming quality about him. If you’re looking for an amazing acupuncturist, Qihui is your person!!

originalText.text: Qihui is a great listener and knowledgeable practitioner. He goes the extra mile to help you find answers to unlocking your best health. I always leave feeling a good calm energy.

originalText.text: Since the pandemic my sleeping habits has gone haywire and endless sleep debt. I was  struggling to stay focus, low in energy and and I know it impacted other functions like my eczema to flare up. I came across Dr. Qin through another TCM practitioner in the summer, after the initial consultation, he started to work on strengthening my spleen, digestion, and circulation. I also did my best to sleep before 12am and avoid cold fluids. Dr. Qin is really patient and attentive, asks questions before each session starts so he can properly assess the conditions. He has very extensive knowledge and will explain what he’s going to work on and I’ve learned a lot myself in terms of balancing my mind, body and paying attention to biofeedback. Highly recommend anyone with chronic symptoms, pain and disorders to give acupuncture a chance for healing.

originalText.text: I have been visiting Qihui Jin LAc at The FORCE for over a year and he has exceeded all of my healing expectations! His practice is efficient, cozy, individualized and extremely informed. This has become not only a regular part of my lifestyle, but a pure treat on my journey of self-care and wellness.
